Detailed Description

cvmx_mio_uart::_fcr

The FIFO control register is a write-only register that controls the read- and write-data FIFO operation. When FIFOs and programmable-THRE-interrupt mode are enabled, this register also controls the THRE interrupt-empty threshold level.
